gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Friends have arrived with great joy, they are not crying tears; 
The Maharaj, being wise, says don't worry, I will take care of it.

Here is the translation:

This I am not saying to move forward, took along the saint's bachelor; 
As the evening, as the evening was getting settled, came Master Pipalane to the village.

Here is the translation:

My lord goes with a full stomach, my lord has arrived at the door; 
He said, my lord has sent me a message, go and show it to the saint, come here.

Here is the translation:

Pamya paramanand sukh bhaari, aavya harsana nayane vaari;
Thaya brahmachari romanchite, joee rahya saamu bu pritye.
